Ricoh hits year high then loses momentum . Shares in Ricoh Co Ltd briefly surpassed the high for the year in early Monday morning trade , as investors moved to buy back global issues that were sold off on Friday , brokers said . Its shares were 30 yen higher at 1 , 320 as of 0039 GMT , off from the high of 1 , 350 yen reached soon after the market opened . It was the most heavily traded issue on the first section of the Tokyo bourse in a volume of 2 . 729 million shares . 
